<h1>Sources</h1>
<p>
  Sources are selected from established public-health and food-safety organizations. We favor
  conservative guidance and update dataset metadata when source coverage changes.
</p>
<p>
  Each source is tagged to indicate whether it applies broadly (`all_foods`) or to a specific
  category/food.
</p>
<ul>
  {% for source in sources.items %}
  <li>
    <a href="{{ source.url }}">{{ source.title }}</a> ({{ source.publisher }}) - applies to
    <code>{{ source.applies_to }}</code>
  </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
